cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with semantic segmentation using depth maps. Additionally, it may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as it proposes a novel neural network architecture. The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) as it can be applied to hand-object interaction. Finally, it may belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with processing RGB-D data.
